                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">At EverVerdant Landscaping, our mission is to create sustainable, beautiful outdoor spaces that enhance the natural environment while meeting our clients' aesthetic and functional needs. We believe that landscaping should be both visually stunning and environmentally responsible.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Founded on the principles of sustainability, innovation, and exceptional service, we work closely with each client to develop custom landscaping solutions that reflect their personal style while incorporating eco-friendly practices.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Our commitment to environmental stewardship is evident in every project we undertake, from water conservation strategies to native plant selection and organic maintenance practices.</p>
